Subject: [PATCH 1/1] Add performance counters

---
 driver/linux/driver.h       |  2 ++
 driver/linux/encl.c         | 29 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 driver/linux/ioctl.c        | 11 +++++++++++
 driver/linux/main.c         |  8 ++++++++
 driver/linux/reclaim.c      |  8 ++++++++
